name: The 7 Talisman of Work: Pliers
description:
Welded layers of pure copper. Soldered and bound with ringlets of brass.
Woven from the cosmos and delicately placed in the cracked hands of the tradesman man. 
They have pulled gold.
They have extracted teeth of the enemy.
Hold them with pride and strength.
Honourable to the centre. Elegantly traced from centuries of love.
